        <T extends IGuildChannel> CompletableFuture<T> addChannel(T channel)
        Adds an IGuildChannel to this category.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The type of the channel(type must be a sub type of IGuildChannel) being added to this category.
        Parameters:
        channel - The channel to add to this category.
        Returns:
        A CompletableFuture that completes with the added channel if successful.
